<body class="bg-void-black text-on-background min-h-screen relative overflow-x-hidden font-body-md crt">
<!-- Top AppBar (Suppressed as this is a transactional/success screen, but keeping a minimal brand anchor if needed, though instructions say "hide shell to prioritize Canvas". So we omit standard TopAppBar and BottomNavBar). -->
